<div id="comment_35349404" class="cw">
	<div id="comment_top_35349404" class="commentTop newcomment">
		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_35349404" name="comment_link_35349404" href="//hardware.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2017726&amp;cid=35349404" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(35349404)" >Re:Solution is simple, but not easy</a>


