			<h4><a id="comment_link_35350186" name="comment_link_35350186" href="//hardware.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2017726&amp;cid=35350186" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(35350186)" >Re:This is great news</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_35350186" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 35350186); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Informative)</span></h4>
